
ossfuzz 514727740

Reported 19 May 2026

Abort, crash in _dwarf_destruct_elf_nlaccess

The problem was a double-free, the  free(data);
the one in in read_gs_section_group() was a mistake.
That free is done later via free( ...->gh_content).
the code was revised to  store data
into gh_content within the last month.
That single free(data) was the only such
in read_gs_section_group() and a mistake.
Now as soon as ownership given from data to gh_content
(for a later free())
we  set data=0 and do not free(data).

